snippet.title: Woodo Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Woodo is an upcoming puzzle game with a striking artstyle inspired by wooden construction toys. "With imaginary friend Woodo, we build tiny things bit by bit, immersed in a calm, peaceful world where time stands still." Follow for more: https://twitter.com/YulliaProhorova
